Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:10.65,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.37,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:38.01,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Yami, Asta, Charmy, and Finral \Ncame to report to the Wizard King
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:41.27,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,after their battle at the Underwater Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:42.22,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.22,0:00:43.98,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:48.12,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,The border town of Kiten, which has a history \Nof skirmishes with the Diamond Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.12,0:00:50.15,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,is under attack by a \NDiamond Kingdom squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:57.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's with that massive horde of people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.41,0:00:59.64,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Three of the Eight Shining Generals.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:02.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What are the Eight Shining Generals?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:04.87,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The eight strongest from the Diamond Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:09.25,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,They're similar to the Magic Knights \NCaptains of the Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:18.97,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The first ones to arrive at Kiten \Nin their time of need were...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:20.80,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,That'sâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.38,0:01:24.48,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,The Clover Kingdom's most\Npowerful Magic Knights Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:27.90,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden Dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:33.83,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Yami and the others headed \Nto Kiten as reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:36.82,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.52,0:01:45.16,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make them regret barging into \Nour country with their muddy boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:59.72,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1023,1)}Whoever's Strongest Wins
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:23.86,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you girls sure are cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.86,0:03:27.22,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I know a meadow where there are \Nflowers as beautiful as you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:30.94,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Say, why don't we take a little \Ntrip there with my spatial magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:36.65,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? You look like you \Njust saw something really scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:39.15,main,Girl B,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to murder us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:42.02,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.10,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, la.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:47.25,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Hurry up and get \Nus to the town called Kiten!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:49.50,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But I thought we were off today...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:52.73,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get any time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:55.38,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You can have all the time off \Nyou want once you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:56.79,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:59.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:02.72,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up with the portal \Nalready, you bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:04.99,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, let's see how far you can jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:06.01,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mugging me now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:08.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you, Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:10.22,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so raring to go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:12.32,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,My meal-saving prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:13.03,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What are you even talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:13.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:14.60,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:14.60,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:17.11,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine! Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.81,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Golden Dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:32.47,main,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the advance guard \Nfor the Golden Dawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:34.97,main,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad for a little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:36.38,main,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:41.08,main,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,Such a wretched form for a Shining General.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:42.59,main,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,How unsightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:43.63,main,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,Lagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:46.76,main,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bear to watch. I'll lend you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:49.04,main,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,No one asked for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:51.02,main,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,He's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:57.37,main,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that the people \Nhave great faith in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:59.73,main,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,Lagus! Listen to me when I'm talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:04.65,main,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, let's see if you can protect \Nyourself as well as your people!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.69,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Arrows... Bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:09.41,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.28,0:05:15.29,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Magic: Swift White Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:24.26,main,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:32.51,main,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:35.79,main,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,He easily deflected my fastest \Nlightning-coated arrows
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:37.64,main,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,and even broke through my barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:42.09,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,"See if you can actually protect them"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:43.23,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:45.44,main,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:50.35,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see if {\i1}you{\i0} can protect \Nyourself and your comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:51.80,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:55.29,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno and I are one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:06:00.46,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you ignoring me?\NAt least say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:01.86,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,"Something."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:05.09,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Quit messing with me, you smart-ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:09.40,main,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,Want my help now, Lagus?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:12.23,main,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,How dare he make me look like a fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:16.21,main,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,He's mine! Stay out of my way, Brocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:18.98,main,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,He's mine! You stay out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:20.38,main,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,He's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:21.37,main,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:22.38,main,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:23.93,main,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:25.88,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:28.13,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:29.74,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:33.12,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:38.27,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,The kid I encountered in the \Ndungeon has gotten a lot stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:41.72,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's not fair how fast kids grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:43.36,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Way to make an old man feel older.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:46.05,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,My girls are growing up fast, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.96,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,When they were younger,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:50.73,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,they always said they wanted \Nto marry me when they grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:53.89,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,But now they won't even take baths with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:57.85,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,And they don't want my underwear\Nwashed with their clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.67,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A-Adjutant General Lotus?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:02.66,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,And they say my breath smells like onions...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:13.62,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Steel Creation Magic: Fierce Spiral Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:18.20,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:37.21,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,All these people...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:50.24,main,Yagos,0000,0000,0000,,They're all so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:57.74,italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,His magic keeps clinging to us,\Nmaking our spells not work properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.04,main,Yagos,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:04.66,main,Yagos,0000,0000,0000,,Slime Creation Magic: Mucusnail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:09.67,main,Yagos,0000,0000,0000,,This spell drastically weakens \Nthe magic of anyone it catches.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:13.93,main,Yagos,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never be able to get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:20.77,main,Yagos,0000,0000,0000,,I just love watching powerless \Nweaklings writhe in agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:26.65,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that looks like a\Ntough spell to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:41.91,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I mean, it's pretty \Nuseless against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:45.01,italics,Yagos,0000,0000,0000,,What was that spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:47.08,italics,Yagos,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:56.93,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes... The one thing about this spell\Nis that it sort of destroys anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:02.72,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. I guess someone will \Njust have to rebuild it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:12.97,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... That guy's definitely \Nthe leader of the Golden Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:16.36,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why he's just \Nstanding there. How creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:22.37,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,He's got his grimoire open, so I \Nthink he's using magic, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:26.63,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,All I see is what looks \Nlike tree roots spreading.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:30.15,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,A spell to grow a huge tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:32.63,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds nice and peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:37.67,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no one who could summon a spell \Nbig enough to protect this whole city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:45.33,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,He's using other people's magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:49.67,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I always notice stuff like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:52.94,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Calling the three generals! \NThis is Adjutant General Lotus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:55.24,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy general,\Nthe captain of the Golden Dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:56.86,top,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:58.37,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,seems to be activating a \Nlarge-scale magic attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.04,top,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:09:59.11,top,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.65,top,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:02.12,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least,\Nthe range will include all of Kiten.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:02.12,top,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:07.85,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat! The captain of the Golden Dawn \Nis activating a large-scale magic attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:07.85,italicstop,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,And they're definitely not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:09.88,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? Run?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:14.81,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,The time is at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:17.08,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,The great tree shall now bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:57.76,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this insane magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:02.05,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,World Tree Magic: Great Mistilteinn Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:06.45,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,All for the Clover Kingdom's prosperity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.53,0:11:15.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Kiten.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:20.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, whoa! What the heck is this giant tree?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:22.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Trees like that grow around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:24.68,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think there's giant fruit up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:26.91,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's enough out of you idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:30.82,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This is probably Captain Shiny's spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:33.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?! This is a spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:35.77,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they didn't need us after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:38.42,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Let's go back, then! Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:41.68,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. I'm gonna go check and \Nsee how the battle's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:45.30,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm assuming Captain Shiny's up top.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:50.85,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna head up there. You three help \Nthe townspeople, and try not to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:53.69,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:57.36,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Y-Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:12:01.99,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'm gonna get me \Na piece of that fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:08.24,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta's hurt, and Charmy's... drooling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:10.79,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:18.61,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:22.42,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, there was an incredible \Namount of magic on that battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:25.93,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect this cleaned up most of it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:28.97,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We've suffered a huge loss!\NOur army's basically wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:36.23,main,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,Our army... has basically been wiped out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:38.73,main,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:45.63,main,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,You know what they say \Nabout people who get greedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:47.74,main,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,How unsightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:53.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My arms might be useless,\Nbut I've still got my legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:59.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Please come this way to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:01.46,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Please get on this, la.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:06.47,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt? Please, come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:08.45,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:13.88,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It is our duty as Magic Knights to \Nsave the citizens of the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:15.08,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not busy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:17.60,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,why don't we... get some tea later?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:24.84,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops. If I look down, my tears will...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:29.16,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:33.04,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's going head-to-head with \None of the Diamond guys in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:43.41,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,My meal-saving prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:47.59,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go! My lovely prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:51.03,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, you can \Ndo it, my lovely prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:53.13,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:27.13,italics,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,This young man is so strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:30.09,italics,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,Inconceivable! I'm one of \Nthe Eight Shining Generals!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:36.35,main,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,You shall fall before my beautiful magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:38.10,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:46.27,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Beauty doesn't matter in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:54.81,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever's strongest wins.\NThat's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:14:59.06,main,Lagus,0000,0000,0000,,So beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:05.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He defeated him with a single blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:09.53,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Such a refreshing breeze...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:15.19,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I saw a familiar little speck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:19.16,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:23.40,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That guy joined the Magic Knights \Nthe same time Asta did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:28.02,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention you're all torn up, \Nscrambling around, and soaked with sweat...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:29.78,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:33.14,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He worked his way up into \Nthe Golden Dawn's elite?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.14,0:15:37.01,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he'd make fun of the Black Bulls.\NAll that and he's handsome, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:38.79,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably super popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:42.12,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you're so beat up means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.03,0:15:45.29,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You got stronger again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:46.20,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.31,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not losing to you, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:52.26,italics,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno's... smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:55.00,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:16:00.45,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I-I could eat a hundred bowls \Nof rice along with that smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.07,0:16:05.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking! You got \Ncrazy strong, too, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:09.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose either, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.85,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He's an elite in the Golden Dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:15.87,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,has super powerful magic, \Nand is super handsome...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:19.06,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yet he's competing with Asta,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:22.15,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,a member of the Black Bulls, \Nwho's a meathead with zero magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:27.64,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,They must be great rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.53,0:16:30.17,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:33.34,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:34.63,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.13,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.13,0:16:39.07,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your arms?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:41.32,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Are they gravely hurt?! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.32,0:16:43.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:47.75,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I was worried or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.45,0:16:50.83,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You got hurt because you let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:52.01,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Pay more attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:53.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:56.43,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll heal you immediately \Nwith my recovery magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:17:00.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. Go ahead and \Nheal all the citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:04.36,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my goodness! I shouldn't \Nhave been so forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:05.42,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:09.08,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We don't have \Ntime to deal with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:13.47,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Mimosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:14.53,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:17.21,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, you stay near Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:20.21,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you can't fight \Nwith your arms like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:23.59,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not trying to spoil you or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:25.33,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You can go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:29.61,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:32.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye! Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:47.62,main,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.03,0:17:51.17,main,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,You must be the captain of the Golden Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:56.84,main,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,I had completely underestimated you.\NWho knew you'd have such tremendous magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:18:00.20,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,You've got impressive magic yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:02.06,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to perish in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:04.82,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Take your comrades and leave this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:07.48,main,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:14.79,main,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,Diamond soldiers never retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:20.57,main,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,Red Clay Magic: \NBrilliant Armor Heavy Artillery!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:26.90,main,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,What's that weak little spell supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:33.13,main,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,Let me guess... You must \Nbe out of magic already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:35.19,main,Brocks,0000,0000,0000,,Victory is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.19,0:18:42.61,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,World Tree Magic: Mistilteinn Seed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:46.14,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,You should be honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:51.14,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Your magic has nourished the Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:59.24,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,A Diamond ambush? He must've been \Nhiding with his magic concealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:02.62,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:06.58,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,'Scuse me... Shiny Oddball Masked Dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:08.39,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:11.13,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that if I could manage
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:14.49,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,to bag the Golden Captain,\NI could turn things around, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:22.54,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,To think the guy I fought \Nback then would show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:25.57,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,And he's even stronger now to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:28.71,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop leaving this \Nold guy so far behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:32.96,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you owe me one, Vangeance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:35.02,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me, Yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.51,0:19:38.77,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Ki, was it? How astounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.02,0:19:43.71,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old Diamond dude that I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:45.56,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:48.54,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, really? You don't remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.21,0:19:50.08,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Look. Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:53.00,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no interest in \Nyour filthy-looking chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:54.33,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me cut you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:55.85,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,D'oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:19:58.84,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's it gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:01.59,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,This is definitely bad news...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:05.89,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,But now's the time to show you guys \Nwhat a true Diamond looks like, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:11.38,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:17.14,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't hesitate one bit. I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:24.66,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:29.33,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we're alone in a \Nspot with such a great view,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:33.78,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,why don't we have a little chat, Vangeance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:42.66,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Man, your world tree magic \Nis as impressive as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.66,0:20:45.70,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Please. It's possible thanks \Nto the enemies' magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:51.89,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Right... Your magic {\i1}is{\i0} world tree magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:53.94,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.58,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly what are you trying to say, Yami?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:21:01.89,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm someone who believes his gut instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:04.98,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Vangeance...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:10.12,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Could you take off that mask?
