Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:50.79,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.84,0:22:54.85,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Charmy's Seven Transformations
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.09,0:22:54.13,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Charmy's Seven Transformations!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:22:59.56,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,To all you Charmy Pappitson fans throughout \Nthe world, no... the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.56,0:23:01.10,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,This is the moment you've been waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.10,0:23:06.57,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we'll be answering all your requests \Nto see all those cute Charmy moments!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.57,0:23:08.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:11.17,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Transformation one... Wandering Charmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:12.16,top,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Munchy, munchy, munchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:13.38,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Transformation two...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:15.87,top,Charmy bg,0000,0000,0000,,Deet de-deet de-deet de-deet and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.95,0:23:15.87,sign_33398_297_Festival,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.38,0:23:15.21,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Happi Coat Charmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:17.11,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Transformation three...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.11,0:23:19.37,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Birthday Charmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.01,0:23:20.00,top,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:21.29,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Transformation four...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:23.18,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning God Charmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.18,0:23:24.24,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.24,0:23:25.51,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Transformation five...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.51,0:23:27.43,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Alien Charmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.77,0:23:29.26,top,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La, la, la, la, la, la...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:31.05,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,And last but not least, transformation six...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:33.28,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Merlion Charmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.06,0:23:38.28,top,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La, la, la, la, la, la...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:34.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.87,0:23:36.57,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,So there aren't seven transformations?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.68,0:23:43.39,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see, Asta, how unbelievably \Nstrong I've become?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.39,0:23:47.86,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never going to lose to you... \Nnot in strength, looks, or height!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.86,0:23:51.29,main,yuno,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 53: "Behind the Mask."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.73,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 53\N\N{\fs18} Behind the Mask
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.29,0:23:53.74,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's going \Nto become the Wizard King!
